nodes.text: Unexpected Journeys is an interview with Dave Filoni about the events of the fifth season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars, such as the younglings story arc, Tim Curry replacing the late Ian Abercrombie as the voice of Palpatine, Ahsoka Tano's departure from the Jedi Order and Barriss Offee's fall to the dark side. This article was written by Jonathan Wilkins and published in Star Wars Insider 140. It was later reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2014.
